<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q54_v8" title="Q54_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En una encuesta a 60 estudiantes sobre su colación preferida, 18 prefirieron sándwich, 12 prefirieron fruta, 9 prefirieron yogurt, 7 prefirieron galletas y 14 prefirieron queque.</p>
    <div>
      <p>Si se elige un estudiante al azar, ¿cuál es la probabilidad de que prefiera fruta o queque como colación?</p>
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de estudiantes que prefieren fruta o queque es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que se simplifica a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> equivale a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>13</m:mn>
            <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Los estudiantes que prefieren fruta o queque son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como el total es <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:math>, la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Simplificando por <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>13</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La probabilidad pedida es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> para fruta más <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> para queque, es decir <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que se simplifica a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> no es equivalente a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>325</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>325</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>11</m:mn>
            <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de estudiantes que prefieren fruta o queque es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que la probabilidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> = <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> equivale a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los casos favorables</strong></p>
            <p>Se pide la probabilidad de que un estudiante prefiera fruta o queque.</p>
            <p>Los estudiantes que prefieren fruta son 12 y los que prefieren queque son 14.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar los estudiantes favorables</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>26</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, hay 26 estudiantes favorables.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la probabilidad</strong></p>
            <p>El total de estudiantes es 60, por lo tanto:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>26</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar la fracción</strong></p>
            <p>Como 26 y 60 son divisibles por 2:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>26</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La probabilidad de que un estudiante prefiera fruta o queque es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>